title: Hi there Kira
text:
Welcome to your new website. You probably wonder how you ended up here? Well, it all started with Axel. He wanted us to learn about Openness and now here we are.
Rahel hosts the Play Festival, Meike is eating and you are looking at this blank website. Haha :D
